-color: transparent; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: preserve; text-indent: 35.4pt;&quot;&gt;RF3.2 Selección de estudiante específico.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.39; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: preserve; text-indent: 35.4pt;&quot;&gt;RF3.3 Sincronización en tiempo real entre dispositivos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.39; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: preserve; text-indent: 35.4pt;&quot;&gt;RF3.4 Visualización del trayecto recorrido.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.39; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 35.4pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;RF3.4.1 Diferenciación visual del trayecto.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.39; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;RF3.5 Visualización de la ruta asignada y control de límite.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.39; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: no